English: 

Casey Ryback has now retired from the Navy and is now a chef at 
the Mile High Cafe in Denver, Colorado. Ryback taking his niece 
Sarah Ryback on a vacation. They board a train traveling through 
the Rocky Mountains from Denver to Los Angeles. Travis Dane takes 
the train hostage and starts using the train as a control center 
in his effort to take control of a top-secret government outer space 
super-weapon. Dane built the weapon but was fired by the government 
before it was deployed. He has since hooked up with shadowy Middle 
Eastern terrorists who have offered him 1 billion dollars to use the 
satellite to blow up the Eastern seaboard by targeting a nuclear 
reactor that is located underneath the Pentagon. Dane lets the Pentagon 
know that he&#039;s got control of the weapon by using it to blow up a Chinese
